{"tid":428893,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"間房個書櫃有怪聲","createTime":"2017-10-08T12:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T15:26:57.000Z","uid":108912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5e704f1baf9f3b953cf77c93168efbbc28a4e45d","tid":428893,"uid":108912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"最近到咗夜晚或者凌晨<br />\n都聽到我間房個書櫃傳出怪聲<br />\n應該係個櫃唔夠貼牆，係條罅隙入面傳出<br />\n唔太識形容<br />\n大概係吱吱吱吱或者啾啾啾啾咁樣<br />\n似青蛙或者雀叫，但又細聲啲，低音啲<br />\n每次都短促而有規律咁叫十幾聲就停，大概幾分鐘一次<br />\n嘈又唔算好嘈，但我呢頭算靜，未瞓著點都會聽到，而且個書櫃就係我床邊，多少有啲不安<br />\n好肯定係生物架喇，但唔知係壁虎定昆蟲定其他，我又真係睇唔清楚條罅隙入面有咩<br />\n想問下有冇人屋企有試過咁，或者有頭緒呢種係乜嘢生物，想知道下係咩，確定下係咪害蟲咁"},{"pid":"e4e863bad4d485cf110f995132ee646679fe9a08","tid":428893,"uid":130513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:08:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08175ce5698b7e14e9566594cb6eb81493f33e4f","tid":428893,"uid":19072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:16:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"065db34f71eb4ac3727b728674f99470a8e0552e","tid":428893,"uid":769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:17:53.000Z","msg":"鬼片d劇情需要"},{"pid":"184089002d47e66a296c579491d3b9b6f77a7a6e","tid":428893,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:18:48.000Z","msg":"四腳蛇叫春"},{"pid":"e18b4fed642317a88add8be8c06e464c29964b1b","tid":428893,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:19:28.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a26cc0079c2b8e67109e0b3d7e0d85233c20f9","tid":428893,"uid":137718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:45:48.000Z","msg":"四腳蛇 我屋企都有 夜晚先叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35bfc512a6635d379608b5efbc9a3332dfa58f2","tid":428893,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:31:27.000Z","msg":"多啦A夢"},